    <briefdescription>
<para>Command that requests a state transition. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Encapsulates a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1state_1_1types_1_1StateTransitionRequest" kindref="compound">StateTransitionRequest</ref> and routes it through the command dispatcher to the appropriate <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1state_1_1StateManager" kindref="compound">StateManager</ref>. The command does not execute directly; instead it uses the visitor pattern via accept() to be dispatched.</para>
